cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.DS, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with community detection on graphs using hyperbolic embeddings, which is a problem in machine learning and data mining. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SD (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves clustering algorithms, which falls under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
